to talk about a special book.

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:12.860
This is a book that has lots
of pictures, lots of profiles,

00:00:12.860 --> 00:00:14.670
lots of wisdom in it.

00:00:14.670 --> 00:00:17.426
And you just wish
that when you're

00:00:17.426 --> 00:00:18.800
reading this book
that you didn't

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:21.810
have to pay as much
as the sticker tag,

00:00:21.810 --> 00:00:24.950
because it's
prohibitively expensive.

00:00:24.950 --> 00:00:29.420
But part of the reason is
