00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:57.820
He's taken it beyond that.

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:03.160
And he's put it together in
a very, very authentic voice.

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:06.730
I'm very honored and
very happy that he

00:01:06.730 --> 00:01:08.420
has decided to
come here in person

00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:10.630
and talk to us
about his thoughts.

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:13.960
So without any further
ado, ladies and gentlemen,

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:15.820
please join me in
welcoming William Green.

